  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/8de44419d973c42181b7e584ed4e23dc.poster.avif?t=1748859748\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/8de44419d973c42181b7e584ed4e23dc.webm?t=1748859748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/8de44419d973c42181b7e584ed4e23dc.mp4?t=1748859748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NobodyNowhere is a side-scrolling, story-driven text adventure game in pixel art. The story is set in 2079, when a Replicant awakens in a lab facility amidst a life-or-death situation. The secret replicant aid agency, White Dove, tries to rescue him but fails. In the process they stumble on the real secret of the Replicant project...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/74e1fd713729ce970fabc27be523d80c.webp?t=1748859748\" width=486 height=31 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/5842eea45de4b9c95c43a71dbf104f49.avif?t=1748859748\" width=600 height=210 /></span>Human Science Research Corp is a research organization dedicated to the study of the human body and individual consciousness. Their research focuses on the emergence of individual human thought and the transfer of consciousness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/bcbbf1b6f93d5f7ffe63db559e5ea190.webp?t=1748859748\" width=486 height=31 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/e497c376506dffb695c6d2cf02b9c861.avif?t=1748859748\" width=600 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/b1562e5124f389b71cec2fcc7581fba6.avif?t=1748859748\" width=600 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/a4e18c2d218a51cfcdc6a4d410d835d3.webp?t=1748859748\" width=486 height=31 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as two different characters and investigate the secrets of Human Science Research Corp.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/66850073a0f46e5c560a7b57698c44c4.poster.avif?t=1748859748\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/66850073a0f46e5c560a7b57698c44c4.webm?t=1748859748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/66850073a0f46e5c560a7b57698c44c4.mp4?t=1748859748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed pixel animation and fast-paced dialogue create an immersive, animated-movie-like experience.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the world, solve the puzzles with Brain Computer Interface (BCI) and avoid the enemy attacks to find out how the story ends.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Email：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><a href=\"mailto:taghadal@163.com\">taghadal@163.com</a></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/8de44419d973c42181b7e584ed4e23dc.poster.avif?t=1748859748\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/8de44419d973c42181b7e584ed4e23dc.webm?t=1748859748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/8de44419d973c42181b7e584ed4e23dc.mp4?t=1748859748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NobodyNowhere is a side-scrolling, story-driven text adventure game in pixel art. The story is set in 2079, when a Replicant awakens in a lab facility amidst a life-or-death situation. The secret replicant aid agency, White Dove, tries to rescue him but fails. In the process they stumble on the real secret of the Replicant project...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/74e1fd713729ce970fabc27be523d80c.webp?t=1748859748\" width=486 height=31 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/5842eea45de4b9c95c43a71dbf104f49.avif?t=1748859748\" width=600 height=210 /></span>Human Science Research Corp is a research organization dedicated to the study of the human body and individual consciousness. Their research focuses on the emergence of individual human thought and the transfer of consciousness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/bcbbf1b6f93d5f7ffe63db559e5ea190.webp?t=1748859748\" width=486 height=31 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/e497c376506dffb695c6d2cf02b9c861.avif?t=1748859748\" width=600 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/b1562e5124f389b71cec2fcc7581fba6.avif?t=1748859748\" width=600 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/a4e18c2d218a51cfcdc6a4d410d835d3.webp?t=1748859748\" width=486 height=31 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as two different characters and investigate the secrets of Human Science Research Corp.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/66850073a0f46e5c560a7b57698c44c4.poster.avif?t=1748859748\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/66850073a0f46e5c560a7b57698c44c4.webm?t=1748859748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440890/extras/66850073a0f46e5c560a7b57698c44c4.mp4?t=1748859748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed pixel animation and fast-paced dialogue create an immersive, animated-movie-like experience.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the world, solve the puzzles with Brain Computer Interface (BCI) and avoid the enemy attacks to find out how the story ends.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Email：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><a href=\"mailto:taghadal@163.com\">taghadal@163.com</a></p>",
